headline: Dominion Energy Q3 Earnings & Revenues Beat, '25 EPS Guidance Narrowed
summary: D beats third-quarter earnings and revenue estimates, boosts profits across segments and narrows its 2025 EPS outlook.

headline: Helping Domestic Violence Survivors Rebuild Lives That Feel Like Home
summary: More than 16 million people in the U.S. experience intimate partner violence each year — that's nearly 32 people every minute, according to domestic violence advocacy organization Break the Cycle. To help survivors find safe places to heal, the FirstEnergy Foundation is awarding $100,000 in grants to emergency shelters and housing providers across our service territory.
